*"Oni su se odlučili da krene u kampovanje." (They decided to go camping.)
*"Njih dvoje su odlučili da se venčaju." (The two of them decided to get married.)
*"Mi smo odlučili da pričekamo još malo." (We decided to wait a little bit longer.)
*"Oni su *odlučili* da ne ulaze u tu diskusiju." (They decided not to enter that discussion.)
*"Mi smo *odlučili* da se povučemo s ovog projekta." (We decided to pull out from this project.)